<p><strong>2.</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2941964); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2941964&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663903" alt="M Element" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2941964)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/m-element" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2941964); return false;">M Element</a></span><br />
误打误撞的加了他的QQ好友，他给了我很多翻译上和点子上的帮助。</p>
<p><strong>3.</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agt-leazov" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3006394); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3006394&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663903" alt="Agt_LEAZOV" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3006394)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agt-leazov" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3006394); return false;">Agt_LEAZOV</a></span><br />
