<p><strong>4.</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lovsk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6266435); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6266435&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663903" alt="Lovsk" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6266435)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lovsk" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6266435); return false;">Lovsk</a></span><br />
